name: SST: Super Swithers Target
overview: You are the pilot of a ship that must shoot the alien beings that advance from the top of the screen without being hit by their bombs. As the aliens decrease in number they will advance more and more towards your position. You you manage to finish a pattern then you will have to use a lot of quick reflexes avoiding boulders that fall from above. Published in Italy under the name E.E.D. in Hit Parade C64 n.28 (Novembre 1988) and in Special Program n.45 (luglio/agosto 1988).
